---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about Merc Technologies - 20+ years of precision gauge manufacturing excellence">
  <!-- Company Story -->
  <Section>
    <div class="about-hero">
      <h1>About Merc Technologies</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Since 2003, we've been manufacturing precision gauges for the world's most demanding industries.
        Built on a foundation of technical expertise and unwavering commitment to quality.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Company Story Detailed -->
  <Section>
    <div class="story-content">
      <div class="story-image">
        <div class="image-placeholder image-placeholder-4-3"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="story-text">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
          Merc Technologies was founded in 2003 by a team of precision manufacturing veterans who
          recognized a critical gap in the gauge industry: the need for a manufacturer that could
          deliver both standard and highly customized gauges with the same level of precision and service.
        </p>
        <p>
          What started as a small shop with three employees and a commitment to quality has grown into
          a leading gauge manufacturer serving Fortune 500 companies and precision machine shops alike.
          Our growth has been driven by word-of-mouth recommendations from satisfied customers who
          appreciate our technical expertise, quick turnaround, and unwavering attention to detail.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, we operate from a 25,000 sq ft climate-controlled facility equipped with the latest
          CNC grinding, lapping, and measurement equipment. But our real strength isn't just our
          equipment—it's our people. Our team includes master gauge makers with decades of experience,
          meticulous quality technicians, and application engineers who understand your challenges.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Facility & Capability -->
  <Section className="facility-section">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-lg">Facility & Capabilities</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-2">
      <div class="facility-image">
        <div class="image-placeholder image-placeholder-16-9 mb-md"></div>
        <div class="image-placeholder image-placeholder-16-9"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="facility-details">
        <h3>Manufacturing Excellence</h3>
        <ul class="capability-list">
          <li>
            <strong>25,000 sq ft climate-controlled facility</strong>
            <p>Temperature and humidity controlled to ±2°F and ±5% RH to ensure dimensional stability during manufacturing and inspection.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>State-of-the-art CNC grinding and lapping equipment</strong>
            <p>Latest generation machines capable of holding tolerances to 0.000020" (0.5 microns) with automated in-process gauging.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Full metrology lab with NIST-traceable standards</strong>
            <p>Equipped with air-bearing comparators, optical comparators, CMM, and thread measurement systems for complete dimensional verification.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <Section className="philosophy-section">
    <div class="philosophy-content">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-lg">Our Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="philosophy-grid">
        <div class="philosophy-card card">
          <h3>Precision First</h3>
          <p>
            Quality is never compromised. Every gauge is manufactured to exacting standards and
            100% inspected before it leaves our facility. We don't ship "close enough"—we ship perfect.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-card card">
          <h3>Customer Partnership</h3>
          <p>
            We view ourselves as an extension of your quality team. When you have a challenging
            application, our engineers work with you to develop the optimal solution—even if it
            means recommending a competitor's product when it's a better fit.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-card card">
          <h3>Continuous Improvement</h3>
          <p>
            The gauge industry evolves, and so do we. We continuously invest in new equipment,
            training, and processes to ensure we're delivering the best possible products using
            the most advanced techniques available.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Vision -->
  <Section>
    <div class="vision-content">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-lg">Our Vision</h2>
      <p class="text-center mb-xl" style="max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        We're building Merc Technologies to be the gauge manufacturer that quality professionals
        turn to first—whether they need a simple plug gauge tomorrow or a complex custom solution
        for a unique application.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="vision-item card">
          <h4>Technical Leadership</h4>
          <p>
            Continuing to push the boundaries of what's possible in gauge manufacturing through
            investment in advanced manufacturing technology and metrology equipment.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="vision-item card">
          <h4>Industry Education</h4>
          <p>
            Sharing our expertise through technical seminars, application notes, and one-on-one
            consultation to help raise the quality standards across manufacturing.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="vision-item card">
          <h4>Sustainable Growth</h4>
          <p>
            Expanding our capabilities and capacity while maintaining the attention to detail
            and customer service that built our reputation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Certifications -->
  <Section className="certifications-section">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-lg">Certifications & Standards</h2>
    <div class="certifications-grid">
      <div class="cert-item">
        <div class="cert-icon image-placeholder image-placeholder-1-1"></div>
        <h4>ISO 9001:2015</h4>
        <p>Certified quality management system</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cert-item">
        <div class="cert-icon image-placeholder image-placeholder-1-1"></div>
        <h4>ASME B89.1.5</h4>
        <p>Plain gauge manufacturing standards</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cert-item">
        <div class="cert-icon image-placeholder image-placeholder-1-1"></div>
        <h4>ISO 1938</h4>
        <p>Thread gauge specifications</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cert-item">
        <div class="cert-icon image-placeholder image-placeholder-1-1"></div>
        <h4>NIST Traceable</h4>
        <p>All calibrations and certifications</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <Section className="about-cta">
    <div class="cta-box">
      <h2>Work With Us</h2>
      <p class="mb-lg">
        Ready to experience the Merc Technologies difference? Contact our team to discuss
        your gauge requirements or schedule a facility tour.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <Button href="/contact" large>Get in Touch</Button>
        <Button href="/products" large>View Products</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .story-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .story-text p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .facility-section {
    border-top: var(--border-thick);
    border-bottom: var(--border-thick);
  }

  .capability-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .capability-list li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    border-bottom: var(--border-thin);
  }

  .capability-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .capability-list strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .capability-list p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .philosophy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .philosophy-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .philosophy-card p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .certifications-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .cert-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border: var(--border-thin);
  }

  .cert-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-md);
  }

  .cert-item h4 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .cert-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: var(--font-size-small);
  }

  .cta-box {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border: var(--border-thick);
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
